TEXT 928 -288 Left 2 ;; ===== Gate timing (long charge, long discharge) =====\n; V2 drives PMOS gate: OFF = 12V, ON = 0V\n; ON from 1ms to 21ms (20ms charge window), then OFF\nV2 GP 0 PULSE(12 0 1m 200n 200n 20m 50m)\n \n; V3 drives NMOS gate: keep NMOS OFF the whole time (0V)\nV3 GN 0 0
